                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d647">
                <head>No. 645.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">General <persName type="from">Sickles</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Fish</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1873-11-24">
                            <hi rend="italic">November</hi> 24, 1873</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>If you send order to leave, please instruct me whether I am to reply to Mr.
                    Carvajal’s notes of the 17th and 18th, or make any other communication to this
                    government besides the announcement of my departure. Impression general in
                    Madrid that this matter is settled.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>SICKLES.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
